Issue Identification:
- Identify the application (CRM, ERP, HR system, Jira, Confluence)
- Document specific error message or behavior
- Determine if issue is user-specific or application-wide
- Check when the issue started

Initial Triage:
- Verify application service status
- Check user's access permissions
- Confirm user is using supported browser/version
- Check for recent application updates or changes

{% if app_type == 'crm' %}
CRM Issues (Salesforce, Dynamics, HubSpot):
- Verify user's CRM license and role
- Check object/record permissions
- Clear browser cache and re-login
- Verify integrations are functioning
- Check for workflow/automation errors
- Review recent data imports
{% endif %}

{% if app_type == 'erp' %}
ERP Issues (SAP, Oracle, NetSuite):
- Verify user's authorization roles
- Check connection to ERP server
- Clear local cache/temp files
- Verify required components (Java, GUI client)
- Check for locked transactions
- Review user's company code access
{% endif %}

{% if app_type == 'hr_system' %}
HR System Issues (Workday, SuccessFactors, BambooHR):
- Verify user's HR system access
- Check employee record status
- Review effective-dated permissions
- Clear browser cache
- Check for pending workflow approvals
- Verify SSO integration
{% endif %}

{% if app_type == 'jira' %}
Jira Issues:
- Verify user's Jira license and project access
- Check project permission scheme
- Verify issue security levels
- Clear browser cache
- Check for JQL syntax errors if search issue
- Review workflow status transitions
- Check for plugin conflicts
{% endif %}

{% if app_type == 'confluence' %}
Confluence Issues:
- Verify user's Confluence license
- Check space permissions
- Review page restrictions
- Clear browser cache
- Check for macro errors on page
- Verify attachment size limits
{% endif %}

Troubleshooting Steps:
- Clear browser cache and cookies
- Try in incognito/private mode
- Test with different browser
- Check for JavaScript errors in console
- Verify network connectivity to application
- Check for proxy/firewall issues

Escalation Path:
- Document all troubleshooting attempted
- Escalate to application admin if system issue
- Contact vendor support if needed
- Create internal bug report if defect found

Resolution:
- Document root cause and fix
- Update knowledge base
- Notify user of resolution
- Monitor for recurrence
